#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_lantest.1.md:93
msgid "The following tests are available:"
msgstr "以下のテストが利用可能"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_lantest.1.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**(1) Opening, stating and reading 512 bytes from 1000 files**\n"
": Tests basic file access patterns with many small operations\n"
msgstr ""
"**(1) 1000個のファイルを開き、512バイトを読み出す**\n"
": 多数の小さな操作を伴う基本的なファイルアクセスパターンをテストする\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manpages/man1/afp_lantest.1.md:99
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**(2) Writing one large file**\n"
": Measures sustained write performance\n"
msgstr ""
